en.connect_wallet_to_exhange: Exchange any asset in you Mixin Wallet:
en.authorize_tips: You'll authorize Mixcoin to read your profile.
en.order_will_be_handled: Order will be open when the payment received and you will be notified.
en.confirm_unfavorite_market: Are you sure to unfavorite this market?
en.important_warning: IMPORTANT WARNING: Your price is far from Market Price. Are you sure to continue?
en.deprecated_version_notice: The old version of Mixcoin has been DEPRECATED. If you have some old open orders, you can cancel them here. Enjoy the new version of Mixcoin!
en.you_have_two_ways_to_earn_your_commissio: You have two ways to earn your commission.
en.invitation_commission_rule_1: New user login Mixcoin via your invitation link and create an order, the invitation confirms;
en.invitation_commission_rule_2: When invitee's MAKER orders complete, 50% of the FEE will tranfer to the invitor as Invitation Commission;
en.invitation_commission_rule_3: Invitation link only works in one to one conversation, DO NOT share it in any groups;
en.group_owner_commission_rule_1: Add Mixcoin Bot to your group;
en.group_owner_commission_rule_2: Any MAKER orders created by the group members in the group conversation, 50% of the FEE will transfer to the group owner, as Group Owner Commission;
en.commission_plan_notice_1: Invitation Commission and Group Owner Commission cannot be earned at the same time, Group Owner Commission counts first;
en.commission_plan_notice_2: The final event explanation rights belongs to Mixcoin Team.
en.search_any_asset: Search any asset in your wallet
en.group_admin_notice: You are Group Admin, you can edit group markets that will show to your group member when Mixcoin open in group conversation.

Session {id} is no longer available in memory.

If you happen to run on a multi-process server (like Unicorn or Puma) the process
this request hit doesn't store {id} in memory. Consider turning the number of
processes/workers to one (1) or using a different server in development.

Please make sure a rails development server is running.

zh-CN.connect_wallet_to_exhange: 交易您 Mixin 钱包里的任意加密货币：
zh-CN.authorize_tips: 即将授权 Mixcoin 登录
zh-CN.confirm_cancel_ocean_order: 确定要取消当前委托吗？
zh-CN.order_will_be_handled: 订单在收到转账后会立即处理，请留意机器人的消息提醒
zh-CN.confirm_unfavorite_market: 确定要取消收藏交易对吗？
zh-CN.important_warning: 重要提醒：您的价格偏离市场价过多，确定要下单吗？
zh-CN.deprecated_version_notice: 旧版的 Mixcoin 已经废弃，如果你还有进行中的订单，请在这里取消。欢迎使用全新的 Mixcoin！
zh-CN.you_have_two_ways_to_earn_your_commissio: 您可以通过两种途径赚取佣金。
zh-CN.invitation_commission_rule_1: 新用户点击您的邀请链接登录 Mixcoin 并成功下单后，即视为邀请成功；
zh-CN.invitation_commission_rule_2: 邀请成功后，每当被邀请人独立完成一笔 MAKER 订单，其手续费的 50% 将作为邀请佣金，即时发放；
zh-CN.invitation_commission_rule_3: 邀请链接仅在一对一会话中生效，请不要在任何群中分享邀请链接；
zh-CN.group_owner_commission_rule_1: 将 Mixcoin 机器人拉进您的加密小群；
zh-CN.group_owner_commission_rule_2: 群成员在群内会话打开 Mixcoin 完成的所有 MAKER 订单，手续费 50% 将作为群主佣金，即时发放；
zh-CN.commission_plan_notice_1: 邀请佣金和群主佣金不能叠加，群主佣金优先；
zh-CN.commission_plan_notice_2: 活动最终解释权归 Mixcoin 团队所有。
zh-CN.search_any_asset: 搜索您钱包里的任意加密货币
zh-CN.group_admin_notice: 您是群组管理员。您可以编辑群组交易对，当群成员从群组中打开 Mixcoin 时，将显示群组交易对。
